Package commonj.sdo.helper

Interface Summary
CopyHelper A helper for copying DataObjects.
DataFactory A Factory for creating DataObjects.
DataHelper Data helper methods.
EqualityHelper A helper for comparing DataObjects.
HelperContext This interface represents a helper execution context.
TypeHelper Look up a Type given the uri and typeName or interfaceClass.
XMLDocument Represents an XML Document containing a tree of DataObjects.
XMLHelper A helper to convert XML documents into DataObects and DataObjects into XML documnets.
XSDHelper Provides access to additional information when the Type or Property is defined by an XML Schema (XSD).
